</subSubSection>
<subSubSection pageId="158" pageNumber="159" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="158.[151,1437,1094,1550]" pageId="158" pageNumber="159">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,315,1491,1515]" inLineHeading="true" pageId="158" pageNumber="159" reason="1">Remarks.</emphasis>
There are few records of this porcelain crab. It is difficult to collect because of the speed with which it retreats into cracks between rocks in rubble piles.
</paragraph>
